BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (A wake window is how long baby can stay awake before needing sleep:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (  Newborn \(0-4 wks\):   45-60 minutes) Tj ET
