<< /Length 1528 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SLEEP TRAINING METHODS COMPARISON) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 684.0 Td (1. FERBER METHOD \(Graduated Extinction\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.0 Td (How it works: Put baby down awake, check at increasing intervals) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.0 Td (Day 1: Check at 3, 5, 10, 10, 10 min...) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.0 Td (Day 2: Check at 5, 10, 12, 12, 12 min...) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.0 Td (Day 3: Check at 10, 12, 15, 15, 15 min...) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.0 Td (During checks: Brief verbal comfort, no picking up. 30 seconds max.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.0 Td (Best for: 5+ months, parents who want structure, works in 3-7 days) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 566.2 Td (2. GENTLE/CHAIR METHOD) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 548.2 Td (How it works: Sit in chair next to crib, gradually move farther away) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 534.2 Td (Days 1-3: Chair right next to crib, pat/shush) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 520.2 Td (Days 4-6: Chair halfway across room) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 506.2 Td (Days 7-9: Chair by the door) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 492.2 Td (Days 10-12: Chair outside door \(in hallway\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 478.2 Td (Best for: Anxious babies, parents who can't hear crying, takes 2-3 weeks) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 448.4 Td (3. PICK UP/PUT DOWN) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430.4 Td (How it works: Pick up when crying, put down when calm. Repeat.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 416.4 Td (Best for: Under 6 months, parents who want very gentle approach) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 402.4 Td (Takes longest: 2-4 weeks typically) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
