BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (BEDTIME ROUTINE \(MUST BE CONSISTENT\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Same order, same time, every single night. 20-30 minutes total:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (  Time: ___:___ Start routine) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (  [ ] Bath \(not necessary every night\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (  [ ] Pajamas and diaper) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (  [ ] Feed \(keep baby awake!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (  [ ] Book \(1-2 short books\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.2 Td (  [ ] Song or white noise on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.2 Td (  [ ] Phrase: 'I love you. Time to sleep.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.2 Td (  [ ] Place in crib DROWSY BUT AWAKE) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.2 Td (  Time: ___:___ Baby in crib) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.4 Td (KEY: Baby must go INTO crib awake so they learn to fall asleep there!) Tj ET
endstream
